      <title>新加坡部长在严厉报告后支持美国特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/singapore-minister-sticks-up-for-us-envoy-after-scathing-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿的一个内部监督机构报告称，美国大使乔纳森·卡普兰威胁工作人员，并且未能很好地促进美国在新加坡的利益，新加坡一名高级官员在社交媒体上为美国大使乔纳森·卡普兰辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/singapore-minister-sticks-up-for-us-envoy-after-scathing-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票率创新低，伊朗强硬派收紧议会控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/iran-hard-liners-tighten-parliament-grip-as-turnout-hits-new-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强硬派在选举中巩固了对伊朗议会的控制，选民投票率跌至历史新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/iran-hard-liners-tighten-parliament-grip-as-turnout-hits-new-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:17:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度农民在投票前宣布新一波抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/indian-farmers-announce-a-new-wave-of-protests-ahead-of-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在长达数周的抗议活动因高速公路堵塞而受阻后，数万名农民将于周三搭乘公共交通工具抵达印度首都，这是种植者向政府施加压力以满足他们要求的最新尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/indian-farmers-announce-a-new-wave-of-protests-ahead-of-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国表示立法机构将避免任命外交部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-signals-legislature-will-avoid-naming-new-foreign-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，立法机构在本周的会议上不会宣布任何人事变动，这意味着王毅可能至少在不久的将来继续留任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-signals-legislature-will-avoid-naming-new-foreign-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 05:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AO World 老板表示，保守党减税是不负责任的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/tory-tax-cuts-would-be-irresponsible-says-ao-world-boss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约翰·罗伯茨 (John Roberts) 是在线电器零售商 AO World 的创始人兼首席执行官。 AO World 在伦敦证券交易所上市，截至 2023 年 3 月的一年销售额达 12 亿英镑（15 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/tory-tax-cuts-would-be-irresponsible-says-ao-world-boss</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国自1993年以来首次缺席总理全国人大吹风会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-premier-li-will-not-hold-press-conference-at-npc-breaking-from-tradition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的李强将成为三十年来第一位在年度人大会议上不举行新闻发布会的总理，此举可能会加剧投资者对不透明政策制定的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-premier-li-will-not-hold-press-conference-at-npc-breaking-from-tradition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:54:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超级星期二即将到来，海莉在华盛顿特区初选首次获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/haley-gets-first-primary-win-in-d-c-with-super-tuesday-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[妮基·黑莉 (Nikki Haley) 周日在哥伦比亚特区赢得共和党初选，这让她在 2024 年提名竞赛中取得首场胜利，并减缓了唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 获得共和党提名的进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/haley-gets-first-primary-win-in-d-c-with-super-tuesday-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美韩开始军事演习激怒金正恩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-south-korea-start-military-drills-set-to-anger-kim-jong-un</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和韩国开始了最大规模的年度联合军事演习之一，此举肯定会激怒朝鲜，朝鲜在年初就威胁要摧毁其南部邻国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-south-korea-start-military-drills-set-to-anger-kim-jong-un</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:05:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥候选人谢因鲍姆表示养老金没有面临危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/mexico-candidate-sheinbaum-says-pensions-aren-t-in-danger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统竞选领先者克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆表示，她的政府不会面临养老金消失或改变的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/mexico-candidate-sheinbaum-says-pensions-aren-t-in-danger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 01:40:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将采取法律措施惩罚罢工医生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/south-korea-to-start-legal-steps-to-punish-doctors-in-walkout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国计划启动法律程序，可能会导致对因抗议增加医学院入学率计划而辞职并扰乱医疗保健的医生进行惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/south-korea-to-start-legal-steps-to-punish-doctors-in-walkout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 00:47:37 GMT</pubDate>
